## 例外处理规则

**Agent 被阻塞时：**
收到含 BLOCKED 的消息 → `SendMessage(recipient=依赖方, content=具体问题)`
→ 收到答复 → `SendMessage(recipient=发起方, content=答案)`
→ `TaskUpdate(taskId=被阻塞任务, status="in_progress")`

**协商出现重大分歧时：**
将分歧点写入 `_bmad-output/sprint-{N}/negotiation/conflict-summary.md`
→ `Task(name="party-facilitator")` 读取 party-mode workflow + agent-manifest.csv + conflict-summary.md
→ #yolo 模式产出 consensus-R{N}.md

