## checkpoint.yaml 格式

每个 Sprint 的阶段状态写入 `_bmad-output/sprint-{N}/checkpoint.yaml`：

```yaml
sprint: N
last_updated: 2026-03-01T14:30:00

phases:
  clarification:
    status: done          # not-started | in-progress | done
    output: _bmad-output/sprint-{N}/negotiation/clarification-record.md

  planning:
    status: done
    batch_a: done         # not-started | in-progress | done（Batch A 初始分析）
    batch_b: done         # not-started | in-progress | done（Batch B 交叉评审）
    batch_c: done         # not-started | in-progress | done（Batch C SM 综合）
    output:
      analyst:             _bmad-output/sprint-{N}/negotiation/analyst-perspective.md
      pm:                  _bmad-output/sprint-{N}/negotiation/pm-perspective.md
      architect:           _bmad-output/sprint-{N}/negotiation/architect-perspective.md
      analyst_crossreview: _bmad-output/sprint-{N}/negotiation/analyst-crossreview.md
      pm_crossreview:      _bmad-output/sprint-{N}/negotiation/pm-crossreview.md
      architect_crossreview: _bmad-output/sprint-{N}/negotiation/architect-crossreview.md
      consensus:           _bmad-output/sprint-{N}/negotiation/consensus-R{N}.md

  implementation:
    status: partial       # partial = 有 Story 未完成
    stories:
      story-key-1: done
      story-key-2: ready-for-dev   # 中断续跑入口

  qa:
    status: not-started
    reports:
      security: null
      e2e:      null
      perf:     null

  evolution:
    status: not-started
    output: null
```

**写入时机**（Orchestrator 负责，使用 Write/Edit 工具更新文件）：
- 阶段开始前：将该阶段 status 设为 `in-progress`
- 阶段完成后：将该阶段 status 设为 `done`，填写 output 路径
- 每个 Story / QA 维度完成时：即时更新对应子字段

